526
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:12,859
[SPEAKER_00] to je znak da ne ljubiš Boga.

527
00:25:12,859 --> 00:25:15,660
[SPEAKER_00] Druga postoje napasti u molitvi,

528
00:25:15,660 --> 00:25:17,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne možeš se koncentrirati,

529
00:25:17,460 --> 00:25:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] ne možeš biti...

530
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] Šta to znači?

531
00:25:19,039 --> 00:25:20,059
[SPEAKER_00] Znači da ga ne voliš.

532
00:25:20,059 --> 00:25:22,099
[SPEAKER_00] Kad si s nekim koga voliš,

533
00:25:22,099 --> 00:25:23,440
[SPEAKER_00] ne luta ti um negdje drugdje.

534
00:25:23,440 --> 00:25:24,680
[SPEAKER_00] Tu si s njim.

535
00:25:24,680 --> 00:25:27,140
[SPEAKER_00] Da koji je način?

536
00:25:27,140 --> 00:25:28,940
[SPEAKER_00] A pomozite nam,

537
00:25:28,940 --> 00:25:29,799
[SPEAKER_00] kažeš,

538
00:25:29,799 --> 00:25:30,960
[SPEAKER_00] časni pomozite nam,

539
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:31,859
[SPEAKER_00] kako ćemo ljubiti Boga?

540
00:25:31,859 --> 00:25:33,519
[SPEAKER_00] Evo potičen tvoj duh,

541
00:25:33,519 --> 00:25:34,579
[SPEAKER_00] to mora se dogoditi čudo,

542
00:25:34,579 --> 00:25:37,259
[SPEAKER_00] to je nemoj više skriva svoj tamu,

543
00:25:37,319 --> 00:25:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] iznesi je van.

544
00:25:38,119 --> 00:25:40,160
[SPEAKER_00] Prije svega,

545
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] pred njim,

546
00:25:41,079 --> 00:25:41,900
[SPEAKER_00] idi pred njega.

547
00:25:41,900 --> 00:25:43,339
[SPEAKER_00] Budi gol pred njim.

548
00:25:43,339 --> 00:25:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] To je odmor.

549
00:25:43,920 --> 00:25:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] Bit pred Bogom ono što jesi.

550
00:25:45,500 --> 00:25:46,799
[SPEAKER_00] Napokon se možeš odmoriti.

551
00:25:46,799 --> 00:25:48,680
[SPEAKER_00] Stalno smo u napetosti.

552
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:50,240
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, jedan od težih poslova

553
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:51,400
[SPEAKER_00] koje ljudi rade je gluma.

554
00:25:51,400 --> 00:25:53,019
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što mnogi glumci piju.

555
00:25:53,019 --> 00:25:54,839
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko te zamori.

556
00:25:54,839 --> 00:25:56,140
[SPEAKER_00] A mi smo svi glumci.

557
00:25:56,140 --> 00:25:57,380
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko to umara.

558
00:25:57,380 --> 00:25:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko umara.

559
00:25:58,119 --> 00:25:59,839
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim koja divota kad otkriješ.

560
00:25:59,839 --> 00:26:01,759
[SPEAKER_00] Može biti gol pred Bogom.

561
00:26:01,759 --> 00:26:02,460
[SPEAKER_00] Može biti što jesi.

562
00:26:02,460 --> 00:26:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] On te ljubi.

563
00:26:04,220 --> 00:26:05,220
[SPEAKER_00] Onda imamo ispovjed.

564
00:26:05,220 --> 00:26:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] Daš na jednu dobru ispovjed.

565
00:26:07,380 --> 00:26:08,480
[SPEAKER_00] Kažeš sve.

566
00:26:08,480 --> 00:26:10,900
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko od vas nikad niste se raskrinkali

567
00:26:10,900 --> 00:26:12,099
[SPEAKER_00] u ispovjedi.

568
00:26:12,099 --> 00:26:12,660
[SPEAKER_00] Nikad.

569
00:26:12,660 --> 00:26:13,759
[SPEAKER_00] A to je divno.

570
00:26:13,759 --> 00:26:14,400
[SPEAKER_00] To je divota.

571
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:17,799
[SPEAKER_00] Može se upaliti u tebi napokon.

572
00:26:18,200 --> 00:26:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] da možeš početi ljubiti Boga.

573
00:26:19,599 --> 00:26:20,980
[SPEAKER_00] Svim umom.

574
00:26:20,980 --> 00:26:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] Svim srcem.

575
00:26:21,579 --> 00:26:22,339
[SPEAKER_00] Svim silama.

576
00:26:22,339 --> 00:26:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] Evo tu je život.

577
00:26:23,500 --> 00:26:26,220
[SPEAKER_00] Izvan toga je tama iluzija.

578
00:26:26,220 --> 00:26:27,980
[SPEAKER_00] Evo onda završavam s time.

579
00:26:27,980 --> 00:26:28,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubi Boga.

580
00:26:28,619 --> 00:26:29,640
[SPEAKER_00] I živjet ćeš.

581
00:26:29,640 --> 00:26:31,460
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ljubi lažne bogove.

582
00:26:31,460 --> 00:26:33,400
[SPEAKER_00] I lagano ćeš umirat.

583
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:36,180
[SPEAKER_00] U teškim mukama možemo tako.

584
00:26:36,180 --> 00:26:37,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi su u teškim mukama.

585
00:26:37,279 --> 00:26:38,279
[SPEAKER_00] Zbog toga ne ljubia Boga.

586
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:40,339
[SPEAKER_00] Slušavaju umjetravno težu u svoj život.

587
00:26:40,339 --> 00:26:41,420
[SPEAKER_00] S malo više sporta.

588
00:26:41,420 --> 00:26:42,339
[SPEAKER_00] S malo više zdrave hrane.

589
00:26:42,339 --> 00:26:42,799
[SPEAKER_00] S malo više.

590
00:26:42,799 --> 00:26:43,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nikako.

591
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:44,779
[SPEAKER_00] Nikako taj balans.

592
00:26:44,779 --> 00:26:47,200
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ono što je kraljestvo Božje.

593
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:47,940
[SPEAKER_00] Mir i radost.

594
00:26:47,940 --> 00:26:49,279
[SPEAKER_00] I pravenstvo duhu sve tome.

595
00:26:49,279 --> 00:26:51,420
[SPEAKER_00] Evo kad počnemo ljubiti istinu.

596
00:26:51,420 --> 00:26:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubiti Boga.

597
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koji je divan.

598
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:55,259
[SPEAKER_00] Koji nas je objavio u svom sinu Isusu Hristu.

599
00:26:55,259 --> 00:26:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubeći nas.

600
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:56,920
[SPEAKER_00] Skriža.

601
00:26:56,920 --> 00:26:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kad smo ga razapinjali.

602
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ta ljubav je uskrsla.

603
00:26:59,619 --> 00:27:00,160
[SPEAKER_00] Vječna.

604
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:01,779
[SPEAKER_00] Jedino što naš život vadi.

605
00:27:08,480 --> 00:27:10,480
[UNKNOWN] Hvala.

